# AICOUNTLY Build — root .env.example (developer pointer only).
#
# Real secrets live in server-php/.env (API) and web/.env (Vite).
# This file exists so `grep -r` for env keys inside the repo root
# still surfaces the full list. Copy it to .env for local convenience
# scripts (e.g. docker-compose or shell helpers). Never commit .env.

# See server-php/.env.example for the exhaustive backend key list.
# See web/.env.example for the frontend build-time variables.
